{
  "texts": [
    "Prior research (Dwivedi et al., 2023; Hirunyasiri et al., 2023) has suggested that applying LLMs, such as ChatGPT, enhances the educational experience by providing personalised instructions and immediate feedback.",
    "This feature potentially creates a more engaging learning environment that could facilitate quicker mastery of tasks and improved consistency in task performance.",
    "The observed improvements of participants in learning outcomes can be further explained as follows: The interactive nature of chatbot learning infuses an element of gamification into the educational process.",
    "As (Wu & Yu, 2023) suggests, this aspect makes learning more enjoyable, thereby increasing user engagement.",
    "The 'gamelike' interaction keeps the learners interested, providing a more dynamic, participatory, and effective learning experience."
  ]
}